{"tid":1285981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日經過海富見到伯伯絕食好心痛","createTime":"2019-07-04T17:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T09:43:20.000Z","uid":237370,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e51c0d1403d68051a8d90c3fc22bb25280db3f","tid":1285981,"uid":237370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:47:45.000Z","msg":"借frd ac post<br />\n話說小妹今日經過金鐘見到一班人坐係海富中心門口絕食 為左反送中 反對學生/年青人為暴徒定義 同埋為左防止有人輕生<br />\n當時去已經見到佢地絕食31小時 <br />\n我走過去俾左支寶礦力同朱古力個伯伯 <br />\n伯伯佢見到有朱古力就話佢唔食嘢 唔行收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話你絕食左咁耐 萬一有咩事可以食住頂住先 <br />\n同埋絕食對身體唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n伯伯就好堅持咁望住我話佢唔會有事 神會保佑佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話如果有咩事記得call白車 加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲好多謝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當伯伯望住我嘅時候 我真心好感激好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n伯伯望落去年紀都好大下<br />\n佢仲要為班勇士示威者抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為左香港嘅民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃色衫嘅姐姐同我講一共有四個人絕食<br />\n真係辛苦曬佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你地有機會經過海富可以俾啲野飲俾佢地<br />\n雖然我唔係好同意用絕食依個方法去表達不滿<br />\n但希望佢地都可以健健康康康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋林鄭快撚啲撤回引渡惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry 咁遲先po出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wY1iHje.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwY1iHje.png&h=51a0a8bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSWuOZf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSWuOZf.png&h=9b56c100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"f1089cfa32aefcd0d8c9f7c6e32b873797d54578","tid":1285981,"uid":154054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"唉，個心好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府幾時先肯正面回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再係度偷雞又擺學生上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a92607a24a0f49497aad78799a5e3e6af16093","tid":1285981,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05ae1c03a609c69284ad491a03baa3ec79e287d","tid":1285981,"uid":267782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:56:15.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢請"},{"pid":"7e005d19852eab64fb6207eb132e73e536066e0a","tid":1285981,"uid":237370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PkWKC7p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPkWKC7p.png&h=c815bfa6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9957a0493096830b13d6a4ebfbaa3ce0783de000","tid":1285981,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:14:24.000Z","msg":"真係喊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伯伯你食下野啦"},{"pid":"ed81e7a4a8004bfc5abb03f345d1f7ea01b418f7","tid":1285981,"uid":21028,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:17:44.000Z","msg":"啱 抗爭唔係要輕生 <br />\n香港人 要撐自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60752d0545ea9f6a958e1497cfda7989fcb2a03b","tid":1285981,"uid":268480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"阿伯好老⋯⋯仲要絕食⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我無野講"},{"pid":"c355f4a352a0f4b4d8b8e20d59983b96a26e0d54","tid":1285981,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:51:08.000Z","msg":"而家現場夠唔夠野飲？"},{"pid":"1b5de31191d0aeeeb9e805efd9d35268b7d87449","tid":1285981,"uid":197090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f91541d435c3c1aeb76ed418437b1fd96288f3d","tid":1285981,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"咩佢重未'X'咩， 唔講得出黎，廢時比人話五毛，但真係忍唔住問"}]}